# Amazon BedRock- RAG

RAG = Retrival Augmented Generation
Allows a foundation Model to reference a data source outside of training data

Here are the RAG databases

Amazon Opensearch Service :- Search and analytics database realtime similarity queries, store millions of vector embeddings
Amazon Aurora PostgresSQL :- Relational database,Proprietary on AWS
Amazon Neptune Analytics :- Graph database that enable high perforamance graph analytics
Amazon S3 vectore :- cost effective and durable storage with sub secon query perforamnance.


## Usecases
### Customer Service chatbot
Knowledge base:-products features
  RAG application :- chatbot that can answer customer quries

### Legal Research and Analysis
  Knowledge Base - laws, regulations case precedent legal options and expert analysis
  RAG - chatbot that can provide relevant information for specific legal quries 

